Angular CLI commands:

ng new <name> 	... creates new project
ng serve	... starts the angular app at localhost:4200
ng g c <name>	... generates new component
ng g s <name>	... generates new service

Dependency injection
- uplne oddelenie nejakej triedy od inych tried
- dependency sa zaregistruje v poli 'providers' a ak ju chceme niekde pouzit, tak ju posleme do danej triedy
ako parameter v konstruktore. Angular si tam potom vlozi nainicializovanu singleton instanciu


----------------------------------
Forms system
----------------------------------

Features:	- questions with different sorts of answers
			- textarea
			- checkboxes
			- radio buttons
			- ...

		- each form has author, ID, list of question IDs which consist of
		- form for creating questions

